projects.name: Super Store Sales Board

projects.name: AWS Resource Usage Reporting Script
projects.description: Developed a shell script to automate the generation of AWS resource usage reports. Utilized AWS CLI to query and display details for EC2 instances, S3 buckets, RDS instances, Lambda functions, and EBS volumes. Employed jq for JSON processing and formatted output in a tabular format for enhanced readability.

Collected and utilized open-source data.
